network loads (underloaded and overloaded\nregimes). It is superior for the downlink multi-antenna NOUM transmission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Aug 2018 22:22:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 May 2019 15:56:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 19 Sep 2019 18:12:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-23"}
